title: Need help getting gud!
body: Hey everyone! looking for someone who might be willing to help me progress further, I feel like I am stuck where I am at, pointers and assistance would be greatly appreciated! I play mid and adc, a bit of top but can play anywhere if need be, just hoping I can find someone to teach me a few things so I may get better as a player. :)

replies.body: I can help you at least get silver
that would be awesome thanks dude!
Oof, feel free to add me! even if not helping with this!
